        prevention: "Prophylactic factor replacement (prevents hemarthrosis and arthropathy), avoid contact sports (football, hockey, wrestling), use helmets, padding, avoid NSAIDs (ibuprofen, naproxen, aspirin), prompt treatment of bleeds, physical therapy for joints, genetic counseling for carriers, prenatal diagnosis",
