        prevention: "Pre-pregnancy BP control (target <130/80), optimize medications (switch from ACEi/ARB to labetalol, nifedipine, or methyldopa before conception), low-dose aspirin starting 12-28 weeks, weight loss, exercise, low sodium diet, smoking cessation",
