        prevention: "Active management of third stage (oxytocin 10 units IM within 1 minute of delivery, controlled cord traction, uterine massage), treat risk factors (polyhydramnios, macrosomia, multiple gestation, prolonged labor, chorioamnionitis, previa, abruption, prior PPH), prophylactic oxytocin, avoid excessive fundal pressure, repair lacerations promptly",
