        signs: ["Somnolence (arousable)", "Slurred speech", "Ataxia", "Nystagmus (horizontal, vertical)", "Normal pupils (or dilated if co-ingested with anticholinergics)", "Hyporeflexia", "Hypotension (mild)", "Bradycardia (mild)", "Hypothermia (mild)", "Respiratory rate normal or mildly decreased (<12/min, apnea rare unless co-ingested)"],
